### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "user",
  "name": "New User"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### Get a user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/users/677531fcbcacbfa59f293a5f

### Update a user
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/677531fcbcacbfa59f293a5f
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updateduser@example.com",
  "name": "Updated User"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/677531fcbcacbfa59f293a5f

